And in PortletExternalContext.isResonseAllowed lines 224-226

public boolean isResponseAllowed() {
    return isRenderPhase();
}

So EndState will only execute the finalResponseAction if isResponseAllowed() returnes true, but it only returns true during a RenderRequest and redirects can only be sent during ActionRequests.

